            h4.text-center Patron 4: Xav
          .col-sm-8
            .col-sm-12.bhoechie-tab-container
              .col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-4.col-xs-4.bhoechie-tab-menu
                .list-group
                  a.list-group-item.active.text-center(href='#')
                    h4 About
                  a.list-group-item.text-center(href='#')
                    h4 Risks
                  a.list-group-item.text-center(href='#')
                    h4 Step 1
                  a.list-group-item.text-center(href='#')
                    h4 Summary
              .col-lg-8.col-md-8.col-sm-8.col-xs-8.bhoechie-tab
                .bhoechie-tab-content.active
                  p Xav, an outspoken, politically minded twenty-something, uses the library computers to search for jobs. He contributes to many different fora for heated political debates. On Reddit boards, Facebook, and newspaper comments sections, he regularly expresses his opinion in animated way, including in capital letters. Xav also regularly posts personal pictures, such as shots of him partying on the weekend with friends, and has been known to provide status updates about his health.
                .bhoechie-tab-content
                  ol
                    li Unfortunately, Xav’s public and polemical visibility online could be a liability: data analysis tools run by both lenders and potential employers could sift through social networks and other public fora and classify Xav a high risk-individual. This in turn could make it harder for him to get a job, a reasonable rate for a credit card, or obtain a loan. While it’s not easy to tell when he’s been data profiled, the threat of being discriminated against for merely being outspoken is nevertheless a possibility.
                .bhoechie-tab-content
                  p It’s recommended that he protect himself from the data profiling by employers and financial institutions by ensuring he is posting anonymously to online fora and changing social media settings to private.
                .bhoechie-tab-content
                  p Info to be protected
                  ul
                    li Personal information (e.g. Name, DOB, SSN)
                    li Financial information
                    li Employment history
                    li Location information
                    li Social media activity
                    li Online posts
                  p Who is likely to access info against patron’s will?
                  ul
                    li Law enforcement
                    li Corporations
                    li Employer
                    li Potential employers
                    li Banks, lenders, and other financial institutions
                  p What patron is doing/should do to keep their info private?
                  ul
                    li Clear browser history and cookies
                    li Install anti-tracking plug-ins on my browser
                    li Install anti-malware software
